    1. Components

    Footer

    The footer provides links to supplementary information about your service and the ONS, as well as copyright, licensing and other required legal information.

    Open this example in a new tab

    {% from "components/footer/_macro.njk" import onsFooter %}
{{
    onsFooter({
        "cols": [
            {
                "title": 'Legal information',
                "itemsList": [
                    {
                        "text": 'Cookies and privacy',
                        "url": '#0'
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "title": 'About ONS',
                "itemsList": [
                    {
                        "text": 'What we do',
                        "url": '#0'
                    },
                    {
                        "text": 'Contact us',
                        "url": '#0'
                    },
                    {
                        "text": 'Accessibility',
                        "url": '#0'
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "title": 'Statistics',
                "itemsList": [
                    {
                        "text": 'UK Statistics Authority',
                        "url": '#0'
                    },
                    {
                        "text": 'Release calendar',
                        "url": '#0'
                    },
                    {
                        "text": 'News',
                        "url": '#0'
                    }
                ]
            }
        ],
        "OGLLink": {
            "pre": 'All content is available under the',
            "link": 'Open Government Licence v3.0',
            "url": 'https://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/doc/open-government-licence/version/3/',
            "post": ', except where otherwise stated'
        }
    })
}}
    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row 
    {% macro onsFooter(params) %}

    {% from "components/lists/_macro.njk" import onsList %}
    {% from "components/icons/_macro.njk" import onsIcon %}

    {% if params.lang is defined and params.lang %}
        {% set lang = params.lang %}
    {% else %}
        {% set lang = 'en' %}
    {% endif %}

    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy %}
        {% if params.poweredBy.alt is defined and params.poweredBy.alt %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = params.poweredBy.alt %}
        {% else %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = 'Office for National Statistics' %}
        {% endif %}
    {% endif %}

    {% set poweredByLogo %}
   
        {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.poweredBy.logo is defined and params.poweredBy.logo %}
            {{
                onsIcon({
                    "iconType": params.poweredBy.logo,
                    "altText": poweredByAlt
                })
            }}
        {% else %}
            {% if params.lang == 'cy' %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-cy',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Swyddfa Ystadegau Gwladol')
                    })
                }}
            {% else %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-en',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Office for National Statistics')
                    })
                }}
            {% endif %}
        {% endif %}
   
    {% endset %}

    {% set crestLogo %}
        {{
            onsIcon({
                "iconType": 'crest'
            })
        }}
    {% endset %}

    <footer class="ons-footer">

        {% if params.footerWarning is defined and params.footerWarning %}
            {% from "components/panel/_macro.njk" import onsPanel %}
            <div class="ons-footer__warning">
                <div class="ons-container">
                    {% call onsPanel({
                            "type": "warn",
                            "classes": "ons-panel--warn--footer"
                        })
                    %}
                        {{ params.footerWarning | safe }}
                    {% endcall %}
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if params.button is defined and params.button %}
            {% from "components/button/_macro.njk" import onsButton %}
            <div class="ons-footer__button-container ons-u-d-no@m">
                {{
                    onsButton({
                        "id": params.button.id,
                        "type": params.button.type,
                        "classes": params.button.classes if params.button.classes else "",
                        "variants": "ghost",
                        "text": params.button.text,
                        "html": params.button.html,
                        "name": params.button.name,
                        "value": params.button.value,
                        "attributes": params.button.attributes,
                        "url": params.button.url,
                        "buttonStyle": params.button.buttonStyle,
                        "iconType": params.button.iconType,
                        "iconPosition": params.button.iconPosition
                    })
                }}
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ons-footer__body{{ ' ' + params.classes if params.classes else '' }}" data-analytics="footer" {% if params.attributes is defined and params.attributes %}{% for attribute, value in (params.attributes) %}{{attribute}}="{{value}}" {% endfor %}{% endif %}>
            <div class="ons-container{{ ' ons-container--wide' if params.wide }}">
                <div class="ons-grid">
                    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.OGLLink is defined and params.OGLLink %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            {{ poweredByLogo | safe }}
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.language is defined and params.language %}
                        {% set currentLanguage = params.language.languages | selectattr("current") | first %}
                        {% set languageNumber = params.language.languages | length %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col {% if languageNumber and languageNumber != 2 %} ons-u-d-no@m{% elif languageNumber %} ons-u-d-no{% endif %}">
                            {% set languageItems = params.language.languages | rejectattr("current") | list %}
                            {% if currentLanguage.allLanguages is defined and currentLanguage.allLanguages and params.language.allLanguagesUrl is defined and params.language.allLanguagesUrl %}
                                {% set languageItems = (languageItems.push({
                                    "url": params.language.allLanguagesUrl,
                                    "text": currentLanguage.allLanguages,
                                    "lang": currentLanguage.ISOCode
                                }), languageItems) %}
                            {% endif %}
                            {{
                                onsList({
                                    "classes": 'ons-u-mb-no',
                                    "variants": ['bare', 'inline@m'],
                                    "itemsList": languageItems
                                })
                            }}
                        </div>
                        <div class="ons-grid__col {% if languageNumber and languageNumber != 2 %} ons-u-d-no@m{% elif languageNumber %} ons-u-d-no{% endif %} ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.newTabWarning is defined and params.newTabWarning %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col">
                            <p class="ons-u-fs-s ons-u-mb-m">{{ params.newTabWarning | safe }}</p>
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.cols is defined and params.cols %}
                        {% for col in params.cols %}
                            <div class="ons-grid__col ons-col-4@m{{ ' ons-u-mt-m@xxs@m' if loop.index > 1 }}">
                                {% if col.title %}
                                    <h2 class="ons-footer__heading ons-u-fs-r--b">{{ col.title }}</h2>
                                {% endif %}
                                {{
                                    onsList({
                                        "classes": 'ons-u-mb-no',
                                        "variants": 'bare',
                                        "itemsList": col.itemsList
                                    })
                                }}
                            </div>
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.cols is defined and params.cols and params.rows is defined and params.rows %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.rows is defined and params.rows %}
                        {% for row in params.rows %}
                            <!-- Rows -->
                            <div class="ons-grid__col">
                                {{
                                    onsList({
                                        "classes": "ons-footer--rows",
                                        "variants": ["bare", "inline"],
                                        "itemsList": row.itemsList
                                    })
                                }}
                            </div>
                            {% if loop.length > 1 %}
                                {% if not loop.last %}
                                    <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                                        <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                                    </div>
                                {% endif %}
                            {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.OGLLink is defined and params.OGLLink %}
                        <!-- OGL -->
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                        </div>

                        <div class="ons-grid__col">
                            <div class="ons-footer__license">
                                {{
                                    onsIcon({
                                        "iconType": 'ogl'
                                    })
                                }}
                                {% if params.OGLLink.HTML is defined and params.OGLLink.HTML %}
                                    {{ params.OGLLink.HTML | safe }}
                                {% else %}
                                    {% from "components/external-link/_macro.njk" import onsExternalLink %}
                                    {{ params.OGLLink.pre }} {{
                                        onsExternalLink({
                                            "url": params.OGLLink.url,
                                            "linkText": params.OGLLink.link
                                        })
                                    }}{{ params.OGLLink.post }}
                                {% endif %}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.legal is defined and params.legal or params.rows is defined and params.rows and params.OGLLink is not defined or params.OGLLink is not defined and params.legal is not defined and (params.rows is defined and params.rows or params.cols is defined and params.cols) %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.OGLLink is not defined and params.legal is not defined %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col">
                            {{ poweredByLogo | safe }}
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>

                {% if params.legal is defined and params.legal or params.rows is defined and params.rows and params.OGLLink is not defined or params.cols is defined and params.cols and params.OGLLink is not defined %}
                    <div class="ons-grid ons-grid--flex ons-grid--vertical-top ons-grid--between">
                        {% if params.legal is defined and params.legal %}
                            <!-- Legal -->
                            {% for legal in params.legal %}
                                <div class="ons-grid__col">
                                    {{
                                        onsList({
                                            "classes": 'ons-u-mb-m ons-footer--rows',
                                            "variants": ['bare', 'inline'],
                                            "itemsList": legal.itemsList
                                        })
                                    }}
                                    {% if params.crest is defined and params.crest %}
                                        <div class="ons-poweredbylogo ons-u-mb-m">{{ poweredByLogo | safe }}</div>
                                    {% endif %}
                                </div>
                            {% endfor %}
                        {% endif %}

                        {% if params.crest is defined and params.crest %}
                            <!-- Crest -->
                            <div class="ons-grid__col">
                                {{ crestLogo | safe }}
                            </div>
                        {% elif params.legal is defined and params.legal %}
                            <!-- Powered by -->
                            <div class="ons-grid__col">
                                <div class="ons-poweredbylogo">{{ poweredByLogo | safe }}</div>
                            </div>
                        {% endif %}

                    </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if params.copyrightDeclaration is defined and params.copyrightDeclaration %}
                    <!-- Copyright -->
                    <div class="ons-grid"> 
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mt-s">
                            <p class="ons-u-fs-s ons-u-mb-no">&copy; {{ params.copyrightDeclaration.copyright }} <br> {{ params.copyrightDeclaration.text }}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                {% endif %}

            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

{% endmacro %}

    .ons-footer {
  a {
    color: $color-text-banner-link;
    text-decoration: underline;

    &:hover {
      color: $color-text-banner-link-hover;
      text-decoration: underline solid $color-text-banner-link-hover 2px;
    }
  }

  &__button-container {
    background-clip: border-box;
    background-color: $color-header;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  &__warning {
    background-color: $color-banner-bg-dark;
  }

  &__ogl-img {
    margin: 0 0.5rem 0.2rem 0;
    max-width: 100%;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .ons-svg-logo,
  .ons-svg-logo__group {
    fill: $color-black !important;
  }

  &__body {
    background-color: $color-banner-bg;
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;

    .ons-list__link {
      margin-right: 0;
    }

    .ons-poweredbylogo {
      min-height: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  &--rows {
    li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
    }
  }
}

    When to use this component

    You should use the appropriate ONS footer at the bottom of any ONS service.

    Variants

    No OGL

        <div class="ons-grid__col">
          <svg class="ons-svg-logo" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="197" height="19" viewBox="33 2 552 60">
            <title id="ons-logo-en-alt">Office for National Statistics</title>

    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row 
    {% macro onsFooter(params) %}

    {% from "components/lists/_macro.njk" import onsList %}
    {% from "components/icons/_macro.njk" import onsIcon %}

    {% if params.lang is defined and params.lang %}
        {% set lang = params.lang %}
    {% else %}
        {% set lang = 'en' %}
    {% endif %}

    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy %}
        {% if params.poweredBy.alt is defined and params.poweredBy.alt %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = params.poweredBy.alt %}
        {% else %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = 'Office for National Statistics' %}
        {% endif %}
    {% endif %}

    {% set poweredByLogo %}
   
        {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.poweredBy.logo is defined and params.poweredBy.logo %}
            {{
                onsIcon({
                    "iconType": params.poweredBy.logo,
                    "altText": poweredByAlt
                })
            }}
        {% else %}
            {% if params.lang == 'cy' %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-cy',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Swyddfa Ystadegau Gwladol')
                    })
                }}
            {% else %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-en',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Office for National Statistics')
                    })
                }}
            {% endif %}
        {% endif %}
   
    {% endset %}

    {% set crestLogo %}
        {{
            onsIcon({
                "iconType": 'crest'
            })
        }}
    {% endset %}

    <footer class="ons-footer">

        {% if params.footerWarning is defined and params.footerWarning %}
            {% from "components/panel/_macro.njk" import onsPanel %}
            <div class="ons-footer__warning">
                <div class="ons-container">
                    {% call onsPanel({
                            "type": "warn",
                            "classes": "ons-panel--warn--footer"
                        })
                    %}
                        {{ params.footerWarning | safe }}
                    {% endcall %}
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if params.button is defined and params.button %}
            {% from "components/button/_macro.njk" import onsButton %}
            <div class="ons-footer__button-container ons-u-d-no@m">
                {{
                    onsButton({
                        "id": params.button.id,
                        "type": params.button.type,
                        "classes": params.button.classes if params.button.classes else "",
                        "variants": "ghost",
                        "text": params.button.text,
                        "html": params.button.html,
                        "name": params.button.name,
                        "value": params.button.value,
                        "attributes": params.button.attributes,
                        "url": params.button.url,
                        "buttonStyle": params.button.buttonStyle,
                        "iconType": params.button.iconType,
                        "iconPosition": params.button.iconPosition
                    })
                }}
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ons-footer__body{{ ' ' + params.classes if params.classes else '' }}" data-analytics="footer" {% if params.attributes is defined and params.attributes %}{% for attribute, value in (params.attributes) %}{{attribute}}="{{value}}" {% endfor %}{% endif %}>
            <div class="ons-container{{ ' ons-container--wide' if params.wide }}">
                <div class="ons-grid">
                    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.OGLLink is defined and params.OGLLink %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            {{ poweredByLogo | safe }}
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.language is defined and params.language %}
                        {% set currentLanguage = params.language.languages | selectattr("current") | first %}
                        {% set languageNumber = params.language.languages | length %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col {% if languageNumber and languageNumber != 2 %} ons-u-d-no@m{% elif languageNumber %} ons-u-d-no{% endif %}">
                            {% set languageItems = params.language.languages | rejectattr("current") | list %}
                            {% if currentLanguage.allLanguages is defined and currentLanguage.allLanguages and params.language.allLanguagesUrl is defined and params.language.allLanguagesUrl %}
                                {% set languageItems = (languageItems.push({
                                    "url": params.language.allLanguagesUrl,
                                    "text": currentLanguage.allLanguages,
                                    "lang": currentLanguage.ISOCode
                                }), languageItems) %}
                            {% endif %}
                            {{
                                onsList({
                                    "classes": 'ons-u-mb-no',
                                    "variants": ['bare', 'inline@m'],
                                    "itemsList": languageItems
                                })
                            }}
                        </div>
                        <div class="ons-grid__col {% if languageNumber and languageNumber != 2 %} ons-u-d-no@m{% elif languageNumber %} ons-u-d-no{% endif %} ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.newTabWarning is defined and params.newTabWarning %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col">
                            <p class="ons-u-fs-s ons-u-mb-m">{{ params.newTabWarning | safe }}</p>
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.cols is defined and params.cols %}
                        {% for col in params.cols %}
                            <div class="ons-grid__col ons-col-4@m{{ ' ons-u-mt-m@xxs@m' if loop.index > 1 }}">
                                {% if col.title %}
                                    <h2 class="ons-footer__heading ons-u-fs-r--b">{{ col.title }}</h2>
                                {% endif %}
                                {{
                                    onsList({
                                        "classes": 'ons-u-mb-no',
                                        "variants": 'bare',
                                        "itemsList": col.itemsList
                                    })
                                }}
                            </div>
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.cols is defined and params.cols and params.rows is defined and params.rows %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.rows is defined and params.rows %}
                        {% for row in params.rows %}
                            <!-- Rows -->
                            <div class="ons-grid__col">
                                {{
                                    onsList({
                                        "classes": "ons-footer--rows",
                                        "variants": ["bare", "inline"],
                                        "itemsList": row.itemsList
                                    })
                                }}
                            </div>
                            {% if loop.length > 1 %}
                                {% if not loop.last %}
                                    <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                                        <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                                    </div>
                                {% endif %}
                            {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.OGLLink is defined and params.OGLLink %}
                        <!-- OGL -->
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                        </div>

                        <div class="ons-grid__col">
                            <div class="ons-footer__license">
                                {{
                                    onsIcon({
                                        "iconType": 'ogl'
                                    })
                                }}
                                {% if params.OGLLink.HTML is defined and params.OGLLink.HTML %}
                                    {{ params.OGLLink.HTML | safe }}
                                {% else %}
                                    {% from "components/external-link/_macro.njk" import onsExternalLink %}
                                    {{ params.OGLLink.pre }} {{
                                        onsExternalLink({
                                            "url": params.OGLLink.url,
                                            "linkText": params.OGLLink.link
                                        })
                                    }}{{ params.OGLLink.post }}
                                {% endif %}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.legal is defined and params.legal or params.rows is defined and params.rows and params.OGLLink is not defined or params.OGLLink is not defined and params.legal is not defined and (params.rows is defined and params.rows or params.cols is defined and params.cols) %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.OGLLink is not defined and params.legal is not defined %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col">
                            {{ poweredByLogo | safe }}
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>

                {% if params.legal is defined and params.legal or params.rows is defined and params.rows and params.OGLLink is not defined or params.cols is defined and params.cols and params.OGLLink is not defined %}
                    <div class="ons-grid ons-grid--flex ons-grid--vertical-top ons-grid--between">
                        {% if params.legal is defined and params.legal %}
                            <!-- Legal -->
                            {% for legal in params.legal %}
                                <div class="ons-grid__col">
                                    {{
                                        onsList({
                                            "classes": 'ons-u-mb-m ons-footer--rows',
                                            "variants": ['bare', 'inline'],
                                            "itemsList": legal.itemsList
                                        })
                                    }}
                                    {% if params.crest is defined and params.crest %}
                                        <div class="ons-poweredbylogo ons-u-mb-m">{{ poweredByLogo | safe }}</div>
                                    {% endif %}
                                </div>
                            {% endfor %}
                        {% endif %}

                        {% if params.crest is defined and params.crest %}
                            <!-- Crest -->
                            <div class="ons-grid__col">
                                {{ crestLogo | safe }}
                            </div>
                        {% elif params.legal is defined and params.legal %}
                            <!-- Powered by -->
                            <div class="ons-grid__col">
                                <div class="ons-poweredbylogo">{{ poweredByLogo | safe }}</div>
                            </div>
                        {% endif %}

                    </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if params.copyrightDeclaration is defined and params.copyrightDeclaration %}
                    <!-- Copyright -->
                    <div class="ons-grid"> 
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mt-s">
                            <p class="ons-u-fs-s ons-u-mb-no">&copy; {{ params.copyrightDeclaration.copyright }} <br> {{ params.copyrightDeclaration.text }}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                {% endif %}

            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

{% endmacro %}

    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row 
    {% macro onsFooter(params) %}

    {% from "components/lists/_macro.njk" import onsList %}
    {% from "components/icons/_macro.njk" import onsIcon %}

    {% if params.lang is defined and params.lang %}
        {% set lang = params.lang %}
    {% else %}
        {% set lang = 'en' %}
    {% endif %}

    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy %}
        {% if params.poweredBy.alt is defined and params.poweredBy.alt %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = params.poweredBy.alt %}
        {% else %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = 'Office for National Statistics' %}
        {% endif %}
    {% endif %}

    {% set poweredByLogo %}
   
        {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.poweredBy.logo is defined and params.poweredBy.logo %}
            {{
                onsIcon({
                    "iconType": params.poweredBy.logo,
                    "altText": poweredByAlt
                })
            }}
        {% else %}
            {% if params.lang == 'cy' %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-cy',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Swyddfa Ystadegau Gwladol')
                    })
                }}
            {% else %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-en',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Office for National Statistics')
                    })
                }}
            {% endif %}
        {% endif %}
   
    {% endset %}

    {% set crestLogo %}
        {{
            onsIcon({
                "iconType": 'crest'
            })
        }}
    {% endset %}

    <footer class="ons-footer">

        {% if params.footerWarning is defined and params.footerWarning %}
            {% from "components/panel/_macro.njk" import onsPanel %}
            <div class="ons-footer__warning">
                <div class="ons-container">
                    {% call onsPanel({
                            "type": "warn",
                            "classes": "ons-panel--warn--footer"
                        })
                    %}
                        {{ params.footerWarning | safe }}
                    {% endcall %}
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if params.button is defined and params.button %}
            {% from "components/button/_macro.njk" import onsButton %}
            <div class="ons-footer__button-container ons-u-d-no@m">
                {{
                    onsButton({
                        "id": params.button.id,
                        "type": params.button.type,
                        "classes": params.button.classes if params.button.classes else "",
                        "variants": "ghost",
                        "text": params.button.text,
                        "html": params.button.html,
                        "name": params.button.name,
                        "value": params.button.value,
                        "attributes": params.button.attributes,
                        "url": params.button.url,
                        "buttonStyle": params.button.buttonStyle,
                        "iconType": params.button.iconType,
                        "iconPosition": params.button.iconPosition
                    })
                }}
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ons-footer__body{{ ' ' + params.classes if params.classes else '' }}" data-analytics="footer" {% if params.attributes is defined and params.attributes %}{% for attribute, value in (params.attributes) %}{{attribute}}="{{value}}" {% endfor %}{% endif %}>
            <div class="ons-container{{ ' ons-container--wide' if params.wide }}">
                <div class="ons-grid">
                    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.OGLLink is defined and params.OGLLink %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            {{ poweredByLogo | safe }}
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.language is defined and params.language %}
                        {% set currentLanguage = params.language.languages | selectattr("current") | first %}
                        {% set languageNumber = params.language.languages | length %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col {% if languageNumber and languageNumber != 2 %} ons-u-d-no@m{% elif languageNumber %} ons-u-d-no{% endif %}">
                            {% set languageItems = params.language.languages | rejectattr("current") | list %}
                            {% if currentLanguage.allLanguages is defined and currentLanguage.allLanguages and params.language.allLanguagesUrl is defined and params.language.allLanguagesUrl %}
                                {% set languageItems = (languageItems.push({
                                    "url": params.language.allLanguagesUrl,
                                    "text": currentLanguage.allLanguages,
                                    "lang": currentLanguage.ISOCode
                                }), languageItems) %}
                            {% endif %}
                            {{
                                onsList({
                                    "classes": 'ons-u-mb-no',
                                    "variants": ['bare', 'inline@m'],
                                    "itemsList": languageItems
                                })
                            }}
                        </div>
                        <div class="ons-grid__col {% if languageNumber and languageNumber != 2 %} ons-u-d-no@m{% elif languageNumber %} ons-u-d-no{% endif %} ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.newTabWarning is defined and params.newTabWarning %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col">
                            <p class="ons-u-fs-s ons-u-mb-m">{{ params.newTabWarning | safe }}</p>
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.cols is defined and params.cols %}
                        {% for col in params.cols %}
                            <div class="ons-grid__col ons-col-4@m{{ ' ons-u-mt-m@xxs@m' if loop.index > 1 }}">
                                {% if col.title %}
                                    <h2 class="ons-footer__heading ons-u-fs-r--b">{{ col.title }}</h2>
                                {% endif %}
                                {{
                                    onsList({
                                        "classes": 'ons-u-mb-no',
                                        "variants": 'bare',
                                        "itemsList": col.itemsList
                                    })
                                }}
                            </div>
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.cols is defined and params.cols and params.rows is defined and params.rows %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                            {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.legal is defined and params.legal or params.rows is defined and params.rows and params.OGLLink is not defined or params.OGLLink is not defined and params.legal is not defined and (params.rows is defined and params.rows or params.cols is defined and params.cols) %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">

                        <div class="ons-grid__col">
                            {{ poweredByLogo | safe }}
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>

                {% if params.legal is defined and params.legal or params.rows is defined and params.rows and params.OGLLink is not defined or params.cols is defined and params.cols and params.OGLLink is not defined %}
                    <div class="ons-grid ons-grid--flex ons-grid--vertical-top ons-grid--between">
                        {% if params.legal is defined and params.legal %}

                            {% for legal in params.legal %}
                                <div class="ons-grid__col">
                                    {{

                                            "classes": 'ons-u-mb-m ons-footer--rows',

                {% if params.copyrightDeclaration is defined and params.copyrightDeclaration %}

            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row 
    {% macro onsFooter(params) %}

    {% from "components/lists/_macro.njk" import onsList %}
    {% from "components/icons/_macro.njk" import onsIcon %}

    {% if params.lang is defined and params.lang %}
        {% set lang = params.lang %}
    {% else %}
        {% set lang = 'en' %}
    {% endif %}

    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy %}
        {% if params.poweredBy.alt is defined and params.poweredBy.alt %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = params.poweredBy.alt %}
        {% else %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = 'Office for National Statistics' %}
        {% endif %}
    {% endif %}

    {% set poweredByLogo %}
   
        {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.poweredBy.logo is defined and params.poweredBy.logo %}
            {{
                onsIcon({
                    "iconType": params.poweredBy.logo,
                    "altText": poweredByAlt
                })
            }}
        {% else %}
            {% if params.lang == 'cy' %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-cy',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Swyddfa Ystadegau Gwladol')
                    })
                }}
            {% else %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-en',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Office for National Statistics')
                    })
                }}
            {% endif %}
        {% endif %}
   
    {% endset %}

    {% set crestLogo %}
        {{
            onsIcon({
                "iconType": 'crest'
            })
        }}
    {% endset %}

    <footer class="ons-footer">

        {% if params.footerWarning is defined and params.footerWarning %}

                            "type": "warn",
                            "classes": "ons-panel--warn--footer"
                        })
                    %}
                        {{ params.footerWarning | safe }}
                    {% endcall %}
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if params.button is defined and params.button %}
            {% from "components/button/_macro.njk" import onsButton %}
            <div class="ons-footer__button-container ons-u-d-no@m">
                {{
                    onsButton({
                        "id": params.button.id,
                        "type": params.button.type,
                        "classes": params.button.classes if params.button.classes else "",
                        "variants": "ghost",

                        "html": params.button.html,

                        "attributes": params.button.attributes,
                        "url": params.button.url,
                        "buttonStyle": params.button.buttonStyle,
                        "iconType": params.button.iconType,
                        "iconPosition": params.button.iconPosition
                    })
                }}
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ons-footer__body{{ ' ' + params.classes if params.classes else '' }}" data-analytics="footer" {% if params.attributes is defined and params.attributes %}{% for attribute, value in (params.attributes) %}{{attribute}}="{{value}}" {% endfor %}{% endif %}>
            <div class="ons-container{{ ' ons-container--wide' if params.wide }}">
                <div class="ons-grid">
                    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.OGLLink is defined and params.OGLLink %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            {{ poweredByLogo | safe }}
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.language is defined and params.language %}
                        {% set currentLanguage = params.language.languages | selectattr("current") | first %}
                        {% set languageNumber = params.language.languages | length %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col {% if languageNumber and languageNumber != 2 %} ons-u-d-no@m{% elif languageNumber %} ons-u-d-no{% endif %}">
                            {% set languageItems = params.language.languages | rejectattr("current") | list %}
                            {% if currentLanguage.allLanguages is defined and currentLanguage.allLanguages and params.language.allLanguagesUrl is defined and params.language.allLanguagesUrl %}
                                {% set languageItems = (languageItems.push({

    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row 
    {% macro onsFooter(params) %}

    {% from "components/lists/_macro.njk" import onsList %}
    {% from "components/icons/_macro.njk" import onsIcon %}

    {% if params.lang is defined and params.lang %}
        {% set lang = params.lang %}
    {% else %}
        {% set lang = 'en' %}
    {% endif %}

    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy %}
        {% if params.poweredBy.alt is defined and params.poweredBy.alt %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = params.poweredBy.alt %}
        {% else %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = 'Office for National Statistics' %}
        {% endif %}
    {% endif %}

    {% set poweredByLogo %}
   
        {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.poweredBy.logo is defined and params.poweredBy.logo %}
            {{
                onsIcon({
                    "iconType": params.poweredBy.logo,
                    "altText": poweredByAlt
                })
            }}
        {% else %}
            {% if params.lang == 'cy' %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-cy',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Swyddfa Ystadegau Gwladol')
                    })
                }}
            {% else %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-en',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Office for National Statistics')
                    })
                }}
            {% endif %}
        {% endif %}
   
    {% endset %}

    {% set crestLogo %}
        {{
            onsIcon({

    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row 
    {% macro onsFooter(params) %}

    {% from "components/lists/_macro.njk" import onsList %}
    {% from "components/icons/_macro.njk" import onsIcon %}

    {% if params.lang is defined and params.lang %}
        {% set lang = params.lang %}
    {% else %}
        {% set lang = 'en' %}
    {% endif %}

    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy %}
        {% if params.poweredBy.alt is defined and params.poweredBy.alt %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = params.poweredBy.alt %}
        {% else %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = 'Office for National Statistics' %}
        {% endif %}
    {% endif %}

    {% set poweredByLogo %}
   
        {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.poweredBy.logo is defined and params.poweredBy.logo %}
            {{
                onsIcon({
                    "iconType": params.poweredBy.logo,
                    "altText": poweredByAlt
                })
            }}
        {% else %}
            {% if params.lang == 'cy' %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-cy',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Swyddfa Ystadegau Gwladol')
                    })
                }}
            {% else %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-en',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Office for National Statistics')
                    })
                }}
            {% endif %}
        {% endif %}
   
    {% endset %}

    {% set crestLogo %}
        {{
            onsIcon({
                "iconType": 'crest'
            })
        }}
    {% endset %}

    <footer class="ons-footer">

                            "type": "warn",

                        {{ params.footerWarning | safe }}

                </div>
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if params.button is defined and params.button %}
            {% from "components/button/_macro.njk" import onsButton %}
            <div class="ons-footer__button-container ons-u-d-no@m">
                {{
                    onsButton({
                        "id": params.button.id,
                        "type": params.button.type,
                        "classes": params.button.classes if params.button.classes else "",
                        "variants": "ghost",
                        "text": params.button.text,

                        "attributes": params.button.attributes,
                        "url": params.button.url,
                        "buttonStyle": params.button.buttonStyle,
                        "iconType": params.button.iconType,
                        "iconPosition": params.button.iconPosition
                    })
                }}
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ons-footer__body{{ ' ' + params.classes if params.classes else '' }}" data-analytics="footer" {% if params.attributes is defined and params.attributes %}{% for attribute, value in (params.attributes) %}{{attribute}}="{{value}}" {% endfor %}{% endif %}>
            <div class="ons-container{{ ' ons-container--wide' if params.wide }}">
                <div class="ons-grid">
                    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.OGLLink is defined and params.OGLLink %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            {{ poweredByLogo | safe }}
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.language is defined and params.language %}
                        {% set currentLanguage = params.language.languages | selectattr("current") | first %}
                        {% set languageNumber = params.language.languages | length %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col {% if languageNumber and languageNumber != 2 %} ons-u-d-no@m{% elif languageNumber %} ons-u-d-no{% endif %}">
                            {% set languageItems = params.language.languages | rejectattr("current") | list %}
                            {% if currentLanguage.allLanguages is defined and currentLanguage.allLanguages and params.language.allLanguagesUrl is defined and params.language.allLanguagesUrl %}
                                {% set languageItems = (languageItems.push({
                                    "url": params.language.allLanguagesUrl,
                                    "text": currentLanguage.allLanguages,
                                    "lang": currentLanguage.ISOCode
                                }), languageItems) %}
                            {% endif %}
                            {{
                                onsList({
                                    "classes": 'ons-u-mb-no',
                                    "variants": ['bare', 'inline@m'],
                                    "itemsList": languageItems

                        </div>
                        <div class="ons-grid__col {% if languageNumber and languageNumber != 2 %} ons-u-d-no@m{% elif languageNumber %} ons-u-d-no{% endif %} ons-u-mb-m">

                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">

    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    Name Type Required Description
    OGLLink OGLLink false An object containing settings for the OGL link
    footerWarning string false The content for the footer warning
    copyrightDeclaration copyrightDeclaration false An object containing settings for the Copyright Declaration
    cols Array<FooterCol> false An array of FooterCol objects. Maximum of 3
    rows Array<FooterRow> false An array of FooterRow objects
    legal Array<LegalRow> false An array of LegalRow objects
    poweredBy boolean | PoweredBy false Whether to show the ONS logo, and optionally settings for the logo
    lang string false The current page language. Will change out the ONS logo if poweredBy is provided. Defaults to en
    button Button (ref) false Settings for save and sign out using the button component
    newTabWarning string false Text for warning of links opening in new tabs
    crest boolean false If set to true will add the UK coat of arms to the footer
    wide boolean false If set to true will set a wider page style by adding css to the container

    OGLLink

    Name Type Required Description
    pre string true The text before the OGL link
    url string true The url for the OGL link
    link string true The text of the OGL link
    post string true The text after the OGL link

    CopyrightDeclaration

    Name Type Required Description
    copyright string true The text for the copyright declaration
    text string true The text that comes after the copyright declaration

    FooterCol

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the column
    title string false The title of the column

    FooterRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row

    LegalRow

    Name Type Required Description
    itemsList Array<ListItem> (ref) true A list of links for the row 
    {% macro onsFooter(params) %}

    {% from "components/lists/_macro.njk" import onsList %}
    {% from "components/icons/_macro.njk" import onsIcon %}

    {% if params.lang is defined and params.lang %}
        {% set lang = params.lang %}
    {% else %}
        {% set lang = 'en' %}
    {% endif %}

    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy %}
        {% if params.poweredBy.alt is defined and params.poweredBy.alt %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = params.poweredBy.alt %}
        {% else %}
            {% set poweredByAlt = 'Office for National Statistics' %}
        {% endif %}
    {% endif %}

    {% set poweredByLogo %}
   
        {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.poweredBy.logo is defined and params.poweredBy.logo %}
            {{
                onsIcon({
                    "iconType": params.poweredBy.logo,
                    "altText": poweredByAlt
                })
            }}
        {% else %}
            {% if params.lang == 'cy' %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-cy',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Swyddfa Ystadegau Gwladol')
                    })
                }}
            {% else %}
                {{
                    onsIcon({
                        "iconType": 'ons-logo-en',
                        "altText": poweredByAlt | default('Office for National Statistics')
                    })
                }}
            {% endif %}
        {% endif %}
   
    {% endset %}

    {% set crestLogo %}
        {{
            onsIcon({
                "iconType": 'crest'
            })
        }}
    {% endset %}

    <footer class="ons-footer">

        {% if params.footerWarning is defined and params.footerWarning %}
            {% from "components/panel/_macro.njk" import onsPanel %}
            <div class="ons-footer__warning">
                <div class="ons-container">
                    {% call onsPanel({
                            "type": "warn",
                            "classes": "ons-panel--warn--footer"
                        })
                    %}
                        {{ params.footerWarning | safe }}
                    {% endcall %}
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if params.button is defined and params.button %}
            {% from "components/button/_macro.njk" import onsButton %}
            <div class="ons-footer__button-container ons-u-d-no@m">
                {{
                    onsButton({
                        "id": params.button.id,
                        "type": params.button.type,
                        "classes": params.button.classes if params.button.classes else "",
                        "variants": "ghost",
                        "text": params.button.text,
                        "html": params.button.html,
                        "name": params.button.name,
                        "value": params.button.value,
                        "attributes": params.button.attributes,
                        "url": params.button.url,
                        "buttonStyle": params.button.buttonStyle,
                        "iconType": params.button.iconType,
                        "iconPosition": params.button.iconPosition
                    })
                }}
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ons-footer__body{{ ' ' + params.classes if params.classes else '' }}" data-analytics="footer" {% if params.attributes is defined and params.attributes %}{% for attribute, value in (params.attributes) %}{{attribute}}="{{value}}" {% endfor %}{% endif %}>
            <div class="ons-container{{ ' ons-container--wide' if params.wide }}">
                <div class="ons-grid">
                    {% if params.poweredBy is defined and params.poweredBy and params.OGLLink is defined and params.OGLLink %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col ons-u-mb-m">
                            {{ poweredByLogo | safe }}
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.language is defined and params.language %}
                        {% set currentLanguage = params.language.languages | selectattr("current") | first %}
                        {% set languageNumber = params.language.languages | length %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col {% if languageNumber and languageNumber != 2 %} ons-u-d-no@m{% elif languageNumber %} ons-u-d-no{% endif %}">
                            {% set languageItems = params.language.languages | rejectattr("current") | list %}
                            {% if currentLanguage.allLanguages is defined and currentLanguage.allLanguages and params.language.allLanguagesUrl is defined and params.language.allLanguagesUrl %}
                                {% set languageItems = (languageItems.push({
                                    "url": params.language.allLanguagesUrl,
                                    "text": currentLanguage.allLanguages,
                                    "lang": currentLanguage.ISOCode
                                }), languageItems) %}
                            {% endif %}
                            {{
                                onsList({
                                    "classes": 'ons-u-mb-no',
                                    "variants": ['bare', 'inline@m'],
                                    "itemsList": languageItems
                                })
                            }}
                        </div>
                        <div class="ons-grid__col {% if languageNumber and languageNumber != 2 %} ons-u-d-no@m{% elif languageNumber %} ons-u-d-no{% endif %} ons-u-mb-m">
                            <hr class="ons-footer__hr">
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.newTabWarning is defined and params.newTabWarning %}
                        <div class="ons-grid__col">
                            <p class="ons-u-fs-s ons-u-mb-m">{{ params.newTabWarning | safe }}</p>
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if params.cols is defined and params.cols %}
                        {% for col in params.cols %}
                            <div class="ons-grid__col ons-col-4@m{{ ' ons-u-mt-m@xxs@m' if loop.index > 1 }}">
